  <p>Serve as an authoritative yet warm and inviting recourse from the homogenized, algorithm‑driven internet by prioritizing digital autonomy, creativity, privacy, and meaningfulness.</p>

  <h2>Vision</h2>
  <p>Cultivate a hub that educates, inspires, and showcases expertise in JAMstack, IndieWeb, and Digital Gardens—championing a more human‑centric, decentralized web.</p>

  <h2>Values</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Digital Autonomy</strong>: Own your data, identity, and content.</li>
    <li><strong>Creativity & Expression</strong>: Champion unique designs and personal voice.</li>
    <li><strong>Accessibility & Inclusivity</strong>: Make tools and knowledge available to everyone.</li>
    <li><strong>Authenticity & Meaningfulness</strong>: Foster genuine connections and purposeful content.</li>
    <li><strong>Openness & Collaboration</strong>: Share knowledge and build community.</li>
    <li><strong>Quality & Craftsmanship</strong>: Pair technical excellence with clear communication.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What I do</h2>
  <p>Web development (Eleventy/JAMstack), content strategy, copywriting, technical writing, and community‑centered education.</p>

